## 15. claim boundary

claim_allowed:
- nattos is no longer merely an application.
- nattos is a living audit-first runtime platform in early formation.
- nattos has live namespace, live edge, live validators, live runtime gate and evidence-bearing infrastructure.

claim_blocked:
- do not claim full hal complete.
- do not claim full isa complete.
- do not claim full qos complete.
- do not claim complete operating system.
